data.description: Beautiful three bedroom one bath home. Nice open floor plan with a large dining and living area. New HVAC system put in 2021. And a brand new roof put in in 2021. Beautiful covered front porch. Set in the mornings and sip your coffee and enjoy nature. Along with a Wonderful large fenced in backyard. Perfect for grilling and entertaining. Huge shade tree as well. There is also a fabulous sunroom that does have heat and air. It does have windows and a closet as well as an exit door. Could definitely be an office or even a small fourth bedroom. Choose whatever you like. newer carpet and fresh paint as well.Basement w/sump pump nice for shelter from storms. Home shows great. Award-winning Mt. Vernon Schools just minutes away from Branson, Missouri and Stockton lake. 2023-10-30
